column2: Origin Agritech Ltd. produces and distributes hybrid crop seeds. The company is headquartered in Beijing, Beijing and currently employs 474 full-time employees. The Company, along with its subsidiaries, is an agricultural biotechnology company. The Company’s segment is Agri-biotech and product development. In addition, State Harvest has built a capacity for breeding technologies, including marker-assisted breeding and doubled haploids technologies. The Company’s activities include the specialization in the research and development.
No. 21 Sheng Ming Yuan Road, Changping District
